        "rich_text": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": {
              "content": "Manus analyzed the Insider Monkey Daily Newsletter from January 5, 2026, producing a comprehensive actionable summary with follow-up links. The analysis covered three main stories: dividend stocks in high-valuation markets, hedge fund AI stock concerns, and Q3 2025 hedge fund investor letters. Key insights included GLP-1 drugs impacting cold storage demand (Americold) and Bath & Body Works as a contrarian value play.",
              "link": null
            },
            "annotations": {
